Goal of this sub project

1. test xa transactions in jbossAS, tomcat, tommee
* nested transactions
* how local transactions could affect XA transaction
2. use Oracle UCP in XA transactions
3. test oracle db and infinispan in XA transaction


setup TOMCAT example
====================

steps:
1. create MY_TEST tablespace
2. run script setup_db_schema.sql as db system user
3. get tomcat from git repository
4. setup tomcat
4.1 set the db connections in conf/server.xml (not the context.xml!)
4.1.1 url ip address
4.1.2 user name and password if different schemas used
4.2 set correct JAVA_HOME path and CATALINA_HOME in start.sh


